 《合金装备 5》安静演员表示她的设计“根本不实用” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-gear-solid-5-quiet-actor-says-her-design-was-not-practical-at-all-3528011?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=合金装备5-安静演员说她的设计根本不实用Imogen DonovanWed, 01 Nov 2023 14:06:22 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3528011 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你可以有很多其他选择”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-gear-solid-5-quiet-actor-says-her-design-was-not-practical-at-all-3528011">《合金装备 5》后安静的演员表示她的设计“根本不实用”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<em>《合金装备 5：幻痛》</em>中扮演安静的演员斯蒂芬妮·乔斯滕 (Stefanie Joosten) 表示，她的设计“根本不实用”，但仍然扮演着“幻想”的一部分。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/avatar-frontiers-of-pandora-preview-far-cry-james-cameron-3522152">《阿凡达：潘多拉边境》为詹姆斯·卡梅隆的史诗片增添了“孤岛惊魂”的元素</a></strong></li></ul><p>乔斯滕表示，她意识到人们对这个角色有“不同的看法”，并且她“尊重”创作《安静》的艺术性。</p><p> “当然，也可以选择创建一个具有视觉吸引力的角色，”她继续说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3528022" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3528022" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3528022 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2.jpg" alt="《合金装备 5：幻痛》图片来源：Konami" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3528022" class="wp-caption-text"> 《合金装备 5：幻痛》图片来源：Konami</figcaption></figure><p> “我认为电子游戏在某种程度上仍然是你进入的一种幻想世界，所以我绝对尊重关于安静外观的选择，例如，非常具有启发性。”</p><p>相反，Joosten 承认并赞赏有人对她的设计提出了更为批评的意见。</p><p> “这款游戏于 2015 年问世，我认为从那时起，视频游戏格局发生了很大变化。人们正在寻求更多的代表性，我真的明白这一点，”这位演员补充道。</p><p>安静的极简服装在<em>《合金装备 5》</em>的故事中是合理的，因为她对受伤的寄生治疗使她通过皮肤呼吸并进行光合作用获取食物。掩盖对她来说是致命的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3528024" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3528024" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3528024 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3.jpg" alt="《合金装备 5：幻痛》图片来源：Konami" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/metal-gear-solid-quiet-actor-not-practical-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3528024" class="wp-caption-text"> 《合金装备 5：幻痛》图片来源：Konami</figcaption></figure><p> “安静的衣服根本不实用，”乔斯滕反驳道。 “即使有关于她通过皮肤呼吸的解释，当然还有很多其他选择。我确实同意这一点。</p><p> “当我们开始动作捕捉时，我看到了角色艺术作品，当然我的第一反应是，‘这是一套非常暴露的服装’，但我尊重它并接受了它。</p><p> “这基本上就是我的立场。这是幻想，我觉得这也是可以接受的。但我确实理解，我也鼓励女性和所有少数族裔在电子游戏中拥有更多多样化的表现。”</p><p>当时， <em>《合金装备》的</em>创作者表示，一旦给出解释，那些贬低安静设计的人就会“为他们的言行感到羞愧”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，Embark Studios <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-finals-developer-says-ai-allows-for-new-ways-to-work-together-with-voice-actors-3526862">回应了有关在射击游戏中使用人工智能为角色配音的批评</a>：“制作没有演员的游戏并不是最终目标”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-gear-solid-5-quiet-actor-says-her-design-was-not-practical-at-all-3528011">《合金装备 5》后安静的演员表示她的设计“根本不实用”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Sum 41 的最后一张专辑《Heaven :x: Hell》将于明年春天发行https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-final-album-heaven-x-hell-to-arrive-next-spring-3528015?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sum-41-final-专辑天堂x地狱明年春天到来Liberty DunworthWed, 01 Nov 2023 13:48:20 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop-punkRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3528015 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sum 41 乐队的 Deryck Whibley 登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是两个完全不同的记录”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-final-album-heaven-x-hell-to-arrive-next-spring-3528015">Sum 41 后的最后一张专辑《Heaven :x: Hell》将于明年春天发行，并</a>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sum 41 乐队的 Deryck Whibley 登台表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Sum-41@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sum-41">Sum 41</a>宣布了他们即将推出的最终专辑《Heaven :x: Hell》的详细信息，并确认该专辑预计将于 2024 年春季发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/july-6-braincellsdoes-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-deryck-whibley-sum-41-2521197">摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ – 德里克·惠布利，Sum 41</a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-to-return-to-pop-punk-roots-on-new-double-album-heaven-and-hell-3189561">去年首次宣布即将发行专辑的消息</a>，并在两个月前分享了新单曲 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-return-with-ferocious-new-single-landmines-3505161">“Landmines”</a> 。这张唱片将标志着他们自 2019 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-new-album-order-in-decline-single-out-for-blood-2480821">《Order in Decline》</a>以来第八次录音室发行，也是第一张完整专辑。</p><p> Sum 41 还确认《Heaven:x:Hell》将是他们一起发行的最后一张专辑——此前成员们 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-to-split-after-final-album-and-world-tour-3440842">透露了他们在完成全球巡演后计划解散的消息。</a></p><p>现在，主唱 Deryck Whibley 透露了即将发行的专辑预计何时发布，并透露了歌迷们对最终版本的期望声音。</p><p> “目前还没有发布日期，”他在接受德克萨斯广播电台<em>94.5 The Buzz</em> （来自<a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/sum-41s-new-album-heaven-x-hell-to-arrive-in-spring-2024" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blabbermouth</em></a> ）采访时说道。 “我有预感，可能会是明年初，有点像春天。那就是我所想的。所有这些事情现在都在解决中。”</p><p>他继续说道，并补充说这张专辑的发行将就像两张不同的唱片合二为一——“天堂”一面听起来像他们早期的流行朋克，而“地狱”一面听起来像他们最近的唱片。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sum 41 - 地雷（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eQEY1gPeZgk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “这是两个完全不同的记录。每面有10首歌曲。我将早期的 Sum 41 流行朋克称为“天堂”，而“地狱”则类似于更新、更重的 Sum 41，我们在过去的几张唱片中都采用了这种风格，”他解释道。</p><p> “我不想称其为金属，但这是我们所做的事情的版本，它很重且受金属影响，”他补充道。 “多年来，我们两种风格都做过。”</p><p> “我们的重音乐比流行朋克音乐要多，但自从我们在前两张唱片中开始使用重音乐后，就好像你的余生都被贴上了这样的标签。但我们的粉丝并不真正关心任何流行朋克音乐，只喜欢较重的音乐，反之亦然。”</p><p>他还告诉主持人TheresaRockFace，乐队曾一度考虑在专辑中客串，但这些歌曲组合得如此自然，最终没有必要重新创作歌曲。他还补充说，将《Heaven :x: Hell》视为一张双专辑是与成员们心照不宣的一致同意。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sum 41 专访 Deryck Whimbley" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RrDhGE_WWO4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>即将推出的唱片的消息也是在 Whibley <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-has-been-hospitalised-with-pneumonia-3498859">因肺炎治疗</a>后于 9 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-discharged-from-hospital-following-pneumonia-infection-3499258">出院</a>后传出的。</p><p> “我还没有脱离困境，并被告知要为接下来几周的过山车病做好准备，我保持积极态度并尽最大努力度过这一切，” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-shares-health-update-following-hospitalisation-3500564">他告诉我fans with an update online</a> .</p><p> “I&#39;m still bed ridden, having a hard time breathing, tight chest pains and some pretty wild fever dreams, that I guess are keeping this whole thing somewhat entertaining. I&#39;m in the best hands and am on the right medicine.”</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41-final-album-heaven-x-hell-to-arrive-next-spring-3528015">Sum 41&#39;s final album &#39;Heaven :x: Hell&#39; to arrive next spring</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
